         <abstract>
            <p>Adapting the use of writing stations to the Latin classroom makes the process of reading and editing an integral part of the process of language instruction and learning. Whether used in the foreign language classroom or the English classroom, the use of writing stations makes the process of editing and rewriting less tedious and less isolated.</p>
